caller_intent: Heather wanted to obtain a quote and start a policy for auto and home insurance.
resolution_steps: Agent asked Heather to clarify the type of insurance she needed (auto/home).
Agent inquired if Heather had existing homeowners insurance.
Heather clarified she was not based in Salem, leading to the agent apologizing and ending the call.
summary: Heather called to request auto and home insurance quotes. The agent attempted to clarify her needs but ended the call after realizing service limitations. The conversation indicates a potential need for follow-up or referral to another agent.
